Hereâ€™s a simple Kotlin app for a calculator using Jetpack Compose. The app features basic arithmetic operations: addition, subtraction, multiplication, and division.

First, make sure your build.gradle file is set up for Jetpack Compose:

build.gradle (Project)
gradle
Copy
Edit
